data.description: Welcome to your dream home in South Dawson County! This immaculately maintained residence offers the space and charm you want - in the location that you need!     Enjoy the seamless flow of the open floor plan, where the chef’s kitchen with a view to the family room becomes the heart of the home, perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing with loved ones. The upper level boasts a large daylight filled master bedroom with a large walk-in closet, 3 secondary bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms, alongside a convenient half bath on the main level.    Outside, discover a large fully fenced backyard, offering both privacy and security, while the extended upper deck and expansive waterproof covered patio provide ample space for friends & family, or peace and quiet. The full daylight basement is stubbed for a future bathroom and presents a canvas awaiting your personal touch for future expansion.    Nestled in the coveted Black Mill Preserve, this home offers more than just comfort and convenience. With its close proximity to GA 400, shopping, and schools, every errand or outing is effortlessly accessible. Plus, enjoy the perks of the thriving neighborhood, complete with a sparkling swimming pool and playground, ensuring endless enjoyment for the whole family. Don’t miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own!
